<title>USA: Limited sees Q1 EPS of $0.09/shr with gain.</title>
<headline>Limited sees Q1 EPS of $0.09/shr with gain.</headline>
<dateline>COLUMBUS, Ohio 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Limited Inc said Thursday that it expects to post first quarter earnings of $0.09 per share.</p>
<p>Those projected results include a gain of $0.02 per share from the initial public offering of Brylane, a 26 percent owned specialty catalogue retailer.</p>
<p>The company said that excluding that gain, the $0.07 per share results would be in line with analysts' estimates.</p>
